881
01:16:09,316 --> 01:16:11,860
Fulfill the prophecy.

882
01:16:29,461 --> 01:16:31,254
Morgana, what is it?

883
01:16:53,819 --> 01:16:56,613
What is it?

884
01:17:02,244 --> 01:17:03,954
Aah!

885
01:17:13,964 --> 01:17:15,090
