If we stay calm,
no one will get hurt.

888
01:17:29,980 --> 01:17:31,606
We all wanted
something for nothing.

889
01:17:32,607 --> 01:17:33,692
And that's what they got.

890
01:17:35,986 --> 01:17:39,489
