899
01:18:35,921 --> 01:18:37,422
Depends on what's at stake.

900
01:18:38,215 --> 01:18:39,090
Anything you wish.

901
01:18:40,467 --> 01:18:42,677
The casino would be happy
to offer you unlimited credit

902
01:18:42,677 --> 01:18:44,596
