903
01:18:45,764 --> 01:18:47,682
I have a feeling
you'll do very well.

904
01:18:47,682 --> 01:18:48,934
I can feel it.

905
01:18:49,684 --> 01:18:52,437
Matter of fact,
I can guarantee it.

906
01:18:53,438 --> 01:18:55,857
Save your games
for the people downstairs.

907
01:18:57,692 --> 01:18:58,902
Hm.

908
01:19:03,490 --> 01:19:05,075
