Done.

951
01:22:10,176 --> 01:22:11,678
Gregory!

952
01:22:13,012 --> 01:22:15,140
Oh, God! Gregory!

953
01:22:17,225 --> 01:22:19,727
Oh, God.

954
01:22:21,521 --> 01:22:23,356
You said you'd release him!

955
01:22:23,898 --> 01:22:25,358
